name: Princess Beach Hidden Object - Puzzle & Dress Up
name_original: Princess Beach Hidden Object - Puzzle & Dress Up
description:
Princess is going to the beach for her holiday. She needs to a fashion dressing up. But before dressing up, Let's help princess search the stunning hidden object scenes! Enjoy the quiet soothing surroundings of the beach!

Game features:
- Beautiful hidden object scenes in the beach!
- Search amazing and fun hidden things.
- Each one provides clues to solving the mysteries of the magical map.
- Beautiful Beach girl for you to dress up
- FREE to play!
